t with other hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/53385/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, More', '', 1767369485);
